# duplicate-keys-mixed-types

## Input

```
t web
t 42
t true

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..18
  ENTRY@0..6
    WORD_KEY@0..1
      WORD@0..1 "t"
    SPACE@1..2 " "
    LINE_STRING@2..5
      STRING@2..5 "web"
    NEWLINE@5..6 "\n"
  ENTRY@6..11
    WORD_KEY@6..7
      WORD@6..7 "t"
    SPACE@7..8 " "
    INTEGER@8..10
      NUMERAL@8..10 "42"
    NEWLINE@10..11 "\n"
  ENTRY@11..18
    WORD_KEY@11..12
      WORD@11..12 "t"
    SPACE@12..13 " "
    BOOLEAN@13..17
      TRUE@13..17 "true"
    NEWLINE@17..18 "\n"
```

## AST

```
SourceFile {
    shebang: none,
    items: [
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@0..1 "t",
            },
            value: LineString {
                string: STRING@2..5 "web",
            },
        },
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@6..7 "t",
            },
            value: Integer {
                sign: none,
                numeral: NUMERAL@8..10 "42",
            },
        },
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@11..12 "t",
            },
            value: Boolean {
                token: TRUE@13..17 "true",
            },
        },
    ],
}
```

